snippet.title: Black Border Game Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Download on Google Play Store (FULL) ► https://bit.ly/3s7G00N
Download on Google Play Store (FREE) ► https://bit.ly/3rawjyn
Download on App Store (FULL) ► https://apple.co/3fPoevo
Download on App Store (FREE) ► https://apple.co/3pldxFQ
Download on Steam ► https://bit.ly/2WYtH8O

Website ► https://blackbordergame.com/

Twitter ► https://twitter.com/blackbordergame
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/blackbordergame/
Subscribe for more of Black Border ► https://bit.ly/30OCNq7

Black Border is a border simulator game 🛂 that simulated the life of a real border patrol officer 👮. In this game, you play as a border officer of the border cross entry and exit gates, who supposed to check the passengers' papers and stop the smuggling of illegal items and bribery.

Make sure to leave feedback or anything you believe is worth mentioning in the comments.

Thanks for watching.
